                    "longDescription": "Project Track Backend is an API that facilitates project management through the creation of accounts, communities, and projects. Users can form communities, invite other users to projects, and assign roles with specific permissions. The API also allows for the creation and management of tasks within projects, organized by roles such as Backend and Frontend. Currently in development, it focuses on database logic and permissions, with future plans for integration with a frontend.",
